# Local Helm values overrides (machine/environment specific)
**/values.local.yaml
**/values-*.local.yaml
**/values.*.local.yaml

# Secret values files (keep encrypted variants only if you use them)
**/values.secret.yaml
**/values.secrets.yaml
**/values.secret-*.yaml
**/values.secrets-*.yaml


